public abstract class MapReducePlugin<MAPKEYOUT,MAPVALUEOUT,REDUCEKEYIN,REDUCEVALUEIN,REDUCEKEYOUT,REDUCEVALUEOUT,RESULT>
extends Object
implements PluginInterface

An abstracted map-reduce interface. These interfaces will eventually restrict our plug-ins. Currently, they are just place-holders. Implementation orients itself on HBase's TableMapper, TableReduce.
